# Cursor Rules for Dashboard Checklist Project

## Project Overview
This is a modern dashboard application with checklist functionality built using vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Git Integration
- Repository: https://github.com/Nhumphrey1/dashboard-checklist
- Branch: master
- Remote: origin

## File Structure
- `index.html` - Main application file
- `styles.css` - Styling and animations
- `script.js` - JavaScript functionality
- `README.md` - Project documentation

## Development Guidelines
- Use semantic HTML
- Follow modern CSS practices
- Write clean, documented JavaScript
- Test on multiple browsers
- Ensure responsive design

## Git Workflow
- Commit frequently with descriptive messages
- Use conventional commit format when possible
- Test changes before pushing
- Keep the repository clean and organized 